Package org.jlibsedml.execution

Provides a framework based on the Template pattern to run simulations described by SED-ML.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IModel2DataMappings
    Interface for mappings between simulation results and model identifiers.
    IModelResolver
    Interface for obtaining a model from a given URI.
    IProcessedSedMLSimulationResults
    Specifies processed time-series simulation results following post-processing.
    IRawSedmlSimulationResults
    The single method getMappings () in this class should return an object capable of mapping between the column headings generated by the simulation engine, to the model variable identifiers whose time course is being plotted.
    IXPathToVariableIDResolver
    Defines methods to extract element identifiers from an XPath expression.

Package org.jlibsedml.execution Description

Provides a framework based on the Template pattern to run simulations described by SED-ML.
Clients should extend AbstractSedmlExecutor to hook into this framework.
